      <title>面对通胀上升，美联储对利率和 2024 年降息的看法保持不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/view-fed-leaves-rates-alone-holds-view-2024-cuts-face-elevated-inflation-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三维持利率不变，但政策制定者表示，尽管美联储实现 2% 通胀目标的预期进展较为保守，但他们仍预计到 2024 年底将利率降低四分之三个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/view-fed-leaves-rates-alone-holds-view-2024-cuts-face-elevated-inflation-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
